Range(name), isTest);\n                }\n            } finally {\n                lock.unlock();\n            }\n        }\n\n        long value = getSequenceRange(isTest).getAndIncrement();\n        if (value == -1) {\n            lock.lock();\n            try {\n                for (;;) {\n                    if (getSequenceRange(isTest).isOver()) {\n                        setSequenceRange(sequenceDao.nextRange(name), isTest);\n                    }\n\n                    value = getSequenceRange(isTest).getAndIncrement();\n                    if (value == -1) {\n                        continue;\n                    }\n\n                    break;\n                }\n            } finally {\n                lock.unlock();\n            }\n        }\n\n        if (value < 0) {\n            throw new SequenceException(\"Sequence value overflow, value = \" + value);\n        }\n\n        return value;\n    }", "signature": "long nextValue()", "full_signature": "@Override public long nextValue()", "class_method_signature": "GroupSequence.nextValue()", "testcase": false, "constructor": false, "invocations": ["isTestSeq", "getSequenceRange", "lock", "getSequenceRange", "setSequenceRange", "nextRange", "unlock", "getAndIncrement", "getSequenceRange", "lock", "isOver", "getSequenceRange", "setSequenceRange", "nextRange", "getAndIncrement", "getSequenceRange", "unlock"]}, "repository": {"repo_id": 42987615, "url": "https://github.com/loye168/tddl5", "language": "Java", "is_fork": false, "fork_count": 62, "stargazer_count": 21, "size": 2708, "license": "licensed"}}